{"tid":1742163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[護膚品問題] 孤陋寡聞，其實咁樣算唔算呃秤？？","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T11:00:17.000Z","uid":130563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ab1ef1ca57db7287f11b31bb4e866cf6e7f43c","tid":1742163,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"事源身邊有人去旅行，去完送咗支潤膚膏俾家母，聽講佢用咗幾日就用完，<br />\n佢就咁我扑爆佢睇下個實際容量，<br />\n<br />\n支野成隻手咁長，但係實際volume都係得手指尾頭咁多多，我覺得好誇張！<br />\n我自己冇接觸開護膚品，孤陋寡聞請問係咪支支都咁痴線？<br />\n<br />\n成支就咁嘅樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZRCdDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZRCdDs.jpg&h=97017d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面寫50g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XW1ywsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXW1ywsR.jpg&h=f54ed30d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拆開就有外殼同內膽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udMuPf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudMuPf6.jpg&h=014eb50b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現原來內膽係通窿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHT1Fnq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHT1Fnq.jpg&h=f51538c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真正裝住潤膚膏嘅地方只有頂部，深度2cm都冇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/20/235441_96b0fc44ead230fdd7c65a3c6bf3d851.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F20%2F235441_96b0fc44ead230fdd7c65a3c6bf3d851.JPG&h=b05dfc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/20/234519_45797cf1d7e49bb3fa7bf7bbc97c2944.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F20%2F234519_45797cf1d7e49bb3fa7bf7bbc97c2944.JPG&h=5539a421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OGywtx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OGywtx.jpg&h=8200c44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個噴嘴都極短<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/20/235155_3f5c189bb68823ee99f8acc9df62c5d7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F20%2F235155_3f5c189bb68823ee99f8acc9df62c5d7.JPG&h=9be7b8ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9698620f7865c475f9bdca7cd0d581e375cd8bee","tid":1742163,"uid":337096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b66e6267e8e423d8e4a2c674b0424762792a80a","tid":1742163,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"咁都得?"},{"pid":"522af4ddcdc0a3aae1ac16a95793f29e4dbc0d00","tid":1742163,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"36f1836b2cb0ba84a4c65121b6c9dfc6234f3ed9","tid":1742163,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:05:36.000Z","msg":"50 g 大約=50 ml<br />\n如果早丶晚搽面和頸，份量約3  ml一天，已好粗用<br />\n<br />\n一支可用10多日"},{"pid":"91129a5f9ff7267b91c5cc70fa9db241b9ee836b","tid":1742163,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f1836b2cb0ba84a4c65121b6c9dfc6234f3ed9","tid":1742163,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:05:36.000Z","msg":"50 g 大約=50 ml<br />\n如果早丶晚搽面和頸，份量約3  ml一天，已好粗用<br />\n<br />\n一支可用10多日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"咁都唔洗整到咁大支架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3adabaa05ce3afd38ca9c2ce02c0a7684d7853","tid":1742163,"uid":159413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"份量同標示唔同先叫呃秤<br />\n呢